Facebook Group Extractor - FB Group Member Finder

CHECKOUT HIGHLIGHTS BELOW TO GET FREE ACCESS TO THE TOOL !!!

A powerful tool to download Facebook group member lists into Excel or CSV format.

Effortless Facebook Research and Analysis
Easily export Facebook group member lists with just one click. Ideal for lead generation and social media research.

Key Features:

Export Facebook group members to CSV and Excel.
Perfect for Facebook research or analysis.
How to Export FB Group Member Lists:

Log in to Facebook.com.
Open Facebook Group Page in Browser.
Click the extension icon from toolbar.
There you will get bunch of options to download in CSV / XLS / Plain Text:

User ID
Username
Profile URL
Profile Picture
Verification Status
Bio Text
